content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1225.25 - Accompaniment by Port Authority employee required for entry into certain areas

State Regulations

No person shall enter any storage room, cashier's room
or cooperage room, at a truck terminal, unless he is accompanied by an employee
of the Port Authority. Notes
